the senator and the socialite : the true story ... the senator and the socialite : ... is the story of reconstruction senator from mississippi blanche bruce . although an excellect book about reconstruction and how an ambitious former slave could posper and become a plantation owner himself and game the corrupt political system to become a u.s . senator , the real story here is about black society , skin color and how one family managed to thrive in it . at least for a couple of generations . this book is an excellent read along with `` redemption '' by nicholas leman